317 internal void WriteEntityRef(string name)
318 {
319 if (_singleStringValue != null)
320 {
321 StartComplexValue();
322 }
323 switch (name)
324 {
325 case "lt":
326 _stringValue.Append('<');
327 break;
328 case "gt":
329 _stringValue.Append('>');
330 break;
331 case "quot":
332 _stringValue.Append('"');
333 break;
334 case "apos":
335 _stringValue.Append('\'');
336 break;
337 case "amp":
338 _stringValue.Append('&');
339 break;

341 _stringValue.Append('&');

344 break;

435 internal void Replay(XmlWriter writer)
436 {
437 if (_singleStringValue != null)

439 writer.WriteString(_singleStringValue);
440 return;

442 for (int i = _firstItem; i <= _lastItem; i++)
443 {

445 switch (item.type)
446 {
447 case ItemType.EntityRef:
448 writer.WriteEntityRef((string)item.data);
449 break;
450 case ItemType.CharEntity:
451 writer.WriteCharEntity((char)item.data);
452 break;
453 case ItemType.SurrogateCharEntity:

456 writer.WriteSurrogateCharEntity(array[0], array[1]);
457 break;

461 break;
462 case ItemType.String:
463 writer.WriteString((string)item.data);
464 break;
465 case ItemType.StringChars:

467 BufferChunk bufferChunk = (BufferChunk)item.data;

487 internal void Trim()
488 {
489 if (_singleStringValue != null)
490 {
491 _singleStringValue = XmlConvert.TrimString(_singleStringValue);
492 return;
493 }
494 string text = _stringValue.ToString();
495 string text2 = XmlConvert.TrimString(text);
496 if (text != text2)
497 {
498 _stringValue = new StringBuilder(text2);
499 }
500 int i;
501 for (i = _firstItem; i == _firstItem && i <= _lastItem; i++)
502 {
503 Item item = _items[i];
504 switch (item.type)
505 {
506 case ItemType.Whitespace:
507 _firstItem++;
508 break;
509 case ItemType.String:
510 case ItemType.Raw:
511 case ItemType.ValueString:
512 item.data = XmlConvert.TrimStringStart((string)item.data);
513 if (((string)item.data).Length == 0)
514 {
515 _firstItem++;
516 }
517 break;
518 case ItemType.StringChars:
519 case ItemType.RawChars:
520 {
521 BufferChunk bufferChunk = (BufferChunk)item.data;
522 int num = bufferChunk.index + bufferChunk.count;
523 while (bufferChunk.index < num && XmlCharType.IsWhiteSpace(bufferChunk.buffer[bufferChunk.index]))
524 {
525 bufferChunk.index++;
526 bufferChunk.count--;
527 }
528 if (bufferChunk.index == num)
529 {
530 _firstItem++;
531 }
532 break;
533 }
534 }
535 }
536 i = _lastItem;
537 while (i == _lastItem && i >= _firstItem)
538 {
539 Item item2 = _items[i];
540 switch (item2.type)
541 {
542 case ItemType.Whitespace:
543 _lastItem--;
544 break;
545 case ItemType.String:
546 case ItemType.Raw:
547 case ItemType.ValueString:
548 item2.data = XmlConvert.TrimStringEnd((string)item2.data);
549 if (((string)item2.data).Length == 0)
550 {
551 _lastItem--;
552 }
553 break;
554 case ItemType.StringChars:
555 case ItemType.RawChars:
556 {
557 BufferChunk bufferChunk2 = (BufferChunk)item2.data;
558 while (bufferChunk2.count > 0 && XmlCharType.IsWhiteSpace(bufferChunk2.buffer[bufferChunk2.index + bufferChunk2.count - 1]))
559 {
560 bufferChunk2.count--;
561 }
562 if (bufferChunk2.count == 0)
563 {
564 _lastItem--;
565 }
566 break;
567 }

570 }

588 private void AddItem(ItemType type, object data)
589 {
590 int num = _lastItem + 1;
591 if (_items == null)
592 {
593 _items = new Item[4];
594 }
595 else if (_items.Length == num)
596 {
597 Item[] array = new Item[num * 2];
598 Array.Copy(_items, array, num);
599 _items = array;
600 }
601 if (_items[num] == null)
602 {
603 _items[num] = new Item(type, data);
604 }
605 else
606 {
607 _items[num].Set(type, data);
608 }
609 _lastItem = num;
610 }

612 internal async Task ReplayAsync(XmlWriter writer)
613 {
614 if (_singleStringValue != null)
615 {
616 await writer.WriteStringAsync(_singleStringValue).ConfigureAwait(continueOnCapturedContext: false);
617 return;
618 }
619 for (int i = _firstItem; i <= _lastItem; i++)
620 {
621 Item item = _items[i];
622 switch (item.type)
623 {
624 case ItemType.EntityRef:
625 await writer.WriteEntityRefAsync((string)item.data).ConfigureAwait(continueOnCapturedContext: false);
626 break;
627 case ItemType.CharEntity:
628 await writer.WriteCharEntityAsync((char)item.data).ConfigureAwait(continueOnCapturedContext: false);
629 break;
630 case ItemType.SurrogateCharEntity:
631 {
632 char[] array = (char[])item.data;
633 await writer.WriteSurrogateCharEntityAsync(array[0], array[1]).ConfigureAwait(continueOnCapturedContext: false);
634 break;
635 }
636 case ItemType.Whitespace:
637 await writer.WriteWhitespaceAsync((string)item.data).ConfigureAwait(continueOnCapturedContext: false);
638 break;
639 case ItemType.String:
640 await writer.WriteStringAsync((string)item.data).ConfigureAwait(continueOnCapturedContext: false);
641 break;
642 case ItemType.StringChars:
643 {
644 BufferChunk bufferChunk = (BufferChunk)item.data;

650 break;
651 case ItemType.RawChars:
652 {
653 BufferChunk bufferChunk = (BufferChunk)item.data;
654 await writer.WriteCharsAsync(bufferChunk.buffer, bufferChunk.index, bufferChunk.count).ConfigureAwait(continueOnCapturedContext: false);
655 break;

1305 internal XmlWellFormedWriter(XmlWriter writer, XmlWriterSettings settings)
1306 {
1307 _writer = writer;
1308 _rawWriter = writer as XmlRawWriter;
1309 _predefinedNamespaces = writer as IXmlNamespaceResolver;
1310 if (_rawWriter != null)
1311 {
1312 _rawWriter.NamespaceResolver = new NamespaceResolverProxy(this);
1313 }
1314 _checkCharacters = settings.CheckCharacters;
1315 _omitDuplNamespaces = (settings.NamespaceHandling & NamespaceHandling.OmitDuplicates) != 0;
1316 _writeEndDocumentOnClose = settings.WriteEndDocumentOnClose;
1317 _conformanceLevel = settings.ConformanceLevel;
1318 _stateTable = ((_conformanceLevel == ConformanceLevel.Document) ? s_stateTableDocument : s_stateTableAuto);
1319 _currentState = State.Start;
1320 _nsStack = new Namespace[8];
1321 _nsStack[0].Set("xmlns", "http://www.w3.org/2000/xmlns/", NamespaceKind.Special);
1322 _nsStack[1].Set("xml", "http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace", NamespaceKind.Special);
1323 if (_predefinedNamespaces == null)
1324 {
1325 _nsStack[2].Set(string.Empty, string.Empty, NamespaceKind.Implied);
1326 }
1327 else
1328 {
1329 string text = _predefinedNamespaces.LookupNamespace(string.Empty);
1330 _nsStack[2].Set(string.Empty, (text == null) ? string.Empty : text, NamespaceKind.Implied);
1331 }
1332 _nsTop = 2;
1333 _elemScopeStack = new ElementScope[8];
1334 _elemScopeStack[0].Set(string.Empty, string.Empty, string.Empty, _nsTop);
1335 _elemScopeStack[0].xmlSpace = XmlSpace.None;
1336 _elemScopeStack[0].xmlLang = null;
1337 _elemTop = 0;
1338 _attrStack = new AttrName[8];
1339 }

1377 public override void WriteDocType(string name, string pubid, string sysid, string subset)
1378 {
1379 try
1380 {
1381 if (name == null || name.Length == 0)
1382 {
1383 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Xml_EmptyName);
1384 }
1385 XmlConvert.VerifyQName(name, ExceptionType.XmlException);
1386 if (_conformanceLevel == ConformanceLevel.Fragment)
1387 {
1388 throw new InvalidOperationException(System.SR.Xml_DtdNotAllowedInFragment);
1389 }
1390 AdvanceState(Token.Dtd);
1391 if (_dtdWritten)
1392 {
1393 _currentState = State.Error;
1394 throw new InvalidOperationException(System.SR.Xml_DtdAlreadyWritten);
1395 }
1396 if (_conformanceLevel == ConformanceLevel.Auto)
1397 {
1398 _conformanceLevel = ConformanceLevel.Document;
1399 _stateTable = s_stateTableDocument;
1400 }
1401 if (_checkCharacters)
1402 {
1403 int invCharIndex;
1404 if (pubid != null && (invCharIndex = XmlCharType.IsPublicId(pubid)) >= 0)
1405 {
1406 string xml_InvalidCharacter = System.SR.Xml_InvalidCharacter;
1407 object[] args = XmlException.BuildCharExceptionArgs(pubid, invCharIndex);
1408 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Format(xml_InvalidCharacter, args), "pubid");
1409 }
1410 if (sysid != null && (invCharIndex = XmlCharType.IsOnlyCharData(sysid)) >= 0)
1411 {
1412 string xml_InvalidCharacter2 = System.SR.Xml_InvalidCharacter;
1413 object[] args = XmlException.BuildCharExceptionArgs(sysid, invCharIndex);
1414 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Format(xml_InvalidCharacter2, args), "sysid");
1415 }
1416 if (subset != null && (invCharIndex = XmlCharType.IsOnlyCharData(subset)) >= 0)
1417 {
1418 string xml_InvalidCharacter3 = System.SR.Xml_InvalidCharacter;
1419 object[] args = XmlException.BuildCharExceptionArgs(subset, invCharIndex);
1420 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Format(xml_InvalidCharacter3, args), "subset");
1421 }
1422 }
1423 _writer.WriteDocType(name, pubid, sysid, subset);
1424 _dtdWritten = true;
1425 }
1426 catch
1427 {
1428 _currentState = State.Error;
1429 throw;
1430 }

1433 public override void WriteStartElement(string prefix, string localName, string ns)
1434 {
1435 try
1436 {
1437 if (localName == null || localName.Length == 0)
1438 {
1439 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Xml_EmptyLocalName);
1440 }
1441 CheckNCName(localName);
1442 AdvanceState(Token.StartElement);
1443 if (prefix == null)
1444 {
1445 if (ns != null)
1446 {
1447 prefix = LookupPrefix(ns);
1448 }
1449 if (prefix == null)
1450 {
1451 prefix = string.Empty;
1452 }
1453 }
1454 else if (prefix.Length > 0)
1455 {
1456 CheckNCName(prefix);
1457 if (ns == null)
1458 {
1459 ns = LookupNamespace(prefix);
1460 }
1461 if (ns == null || (ns != null && ns.Length == 0))
1462 {
1463 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Xml_PrefixForEmptyNs);
1464 }
1465 }
1466 if (ns == null)
1467 {
1468 ns = LookupNamespace(prefix);
1469 if (ns == null)
1470 {
1471 ns = string.Empty;
1472 }
1473 }
1474 if (_elemTop == 0 && _rawWriter != null)
1475 {
1476 _rawWriter.OnRootElement(_conformanceLevel);
1477 }
1478 _writer.WriteStartElement(prefix, localName, ns);
1479 int num = ++_elemTop;
1480 if (num == _elemScopeStack.Length)
1481 {
1482 ElementScope[] array = new ElementScope[num * 2];
1483 Array.Copy(_elemScopeStack, array, num);
1484 _elemScopeStack = array;
1485 }
1486 _elemScopeStack[num].Set(prefix, localName, ns, _nsTop);
1487 PushNamespaceImplicit(prefix, ns);
1488 if (_attrCount >= 14)
1489 {
1490 _attrHashTable.Clear();
1491 }
1492 _attrCount = 0;
1493 }
1494 catch
1495 {
1496 _currentState = State.Error;
1497 throw;
1498 }
1499 }

1502 {

1504 {
1505 AdvanceState(Token.EndElement);

1508 {
1509 throw new XmlException(System.SR.Xml_NoStartTag, string.Empty);
1510 }

1512 {
1513 _elemScopeStack[elemTop].WriteEndElement(_rawWriter);
1514 }

1516 {
1517 _writer.WriteEndElement();

1520 if (_useNsHashtable && prevNSTop < _nsTop)
1521 {
1522 PopNamespaces(prevNSTop + 1, _nsTop);
1523 }
1524 _nsTop = prevNSTop;
1525 if ((_elemTop = elemTop - 1) == 0)
1526 {
1527 if (_conformanceLevel == ConformanceLevel.Document)
1528 {
1529 _currentState = State.AfterRootEle;
1530 }
1531 else
1532 {
1533 _currentState = State.TopLevel;
1534 }
1535 }
1536 }
1537 catch
1538 {
1539 _currentState = State.Error;
1540 throw;
1541 }

1587 public override void WriteStartAttribute(string prefix, string localName, string namespaceName)
1588 {
1589 try
1590 {
1591 if (localName == null || localName.Length == 0)
1592 {
1593 if (!(prefix == "xmlns"))
1594 {
1595 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Xml_EmptyLocalName);
1596 }
1597 localName = "xmlns";
1598 prefix = string.Empty;
1599 }
1600 CheckNCName(localName);
1601 AdvanceState(Token.StartAttribute);
1602 if (prefix == null)
1603 {
1604 if (namespaceName != null && (!(localName == "xmlns") || !(namespaceName == "http://www.w3.org/2000/xmlns/")))
1605 {
1606 prefix = LookupPrefix(namespaceName);
1607 }
1608 if (prefix == null)
1609 {
1610 prefix = string.Empty;
1611 }
1612 }
1613 if (namespaceName == null)
1614 {
1615 if (prefix.Length > 0)
1616 {
1617 namespaceName = LookupNamespace(prefix);
1618 }
1619 if (namespaceName == null)
1620 {
1621 namespaceName = string.Empty;
1622 }
1623 }
1624 if (prefix.Length == 0)
1625 {
1626 if (localName[0] != 'x' || !(localName == "xmlns"))
1627 {
1628 if (namespaceName.Length > 0)
1629 {
1630 prefix = LookupPrefix(namespaceName);
1631 if (prefix == null || prefix.Length == 0)
1632 {
1633 prefix = GeneratePrefix();
1634 }
1635 }
1636 goto IL_01fd;
1637 }
1638 if (namespaceName.Length > 0 && namespaceName != "http://www.w3.org/2000/xmlns/")
1639 {
1640 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Xml_XmlnsPrefix);
1641 }
1642 _curDeclPrefix = string.Empty;
1643 SetSpecialAttribute(SpecialAttribute.DefaultXmlns);
1644 }
1645 else
1646 {
1647 if (prefix[0] != 'x')
1648 {
1649 goto IL_01c9;
1650 }
1651 if (prefix == "xmlns")
1652 {
1653 if (namespaceName.Length > 0 && namespaceName != "http://www.w3.org/2000/xmlns/")
1654 {
1655 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Xml_XmlnsPrefix);
1656 }
1657 _curDeclPrefix = localName;
1658 SetSpecialAttribute(SpecialAttribute.PrefixedXmlns);
1659 }
1660 else
1661 {
1662 if (!(prefix == "xml"))
1663 {
1664 goto IL_01c9;
1665 }
1666 if (namespaceName.Length > 0 && namespaceName != "http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace")
1667 {
1668 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Xml_XmlPrefix);
1669 }
1670 if (!(localName == "space"))
1671 {
1672 if (!(localName == "lang"))
1673 {
1674 goto IL_01c9;
1675 }
1676 SetSpecialAttribute(SpecialAttribute.XmlLang);
1677 }
1678 else
1679 {
1680 SetSpecialAttribute(SpecialAttribute.XmlSpace);
1681 }
1682 }
1683 }
1684 goto IL_020d;
1685 IL_01c9:
1686 CheckNCName(prefix);
1687 if (namespaceName.Length == 0)
1688 {
1689 prefix = string.Empty;
1690 }
1691 else
1692 {
1693 string text = LookupLocalNamespace(prefix);
1694 if (text != null && text != namespaceName)
1695 {
1696 prefix = GeneratePrefix();
1697 }
1698 }
1699 goto IL_01fd;
1700 IL_01fd:
1701 if (prefix.Length != 0)
1702 {
1703 PushNamespaceImplicit(prefix, namespaceName);
1704 }
1705 goto IL_020d;
1706 IL_020d:
1707 AddAttribute(prefix, localName, namespaceName);
1708 if (_specAttr == SpecialAttribute.No)
1709 {
1710 _writer.WriteStartAttribute(prefix, localName, namespaceName);
1711 }
1712 }
1713 catch
1714 {
1715 _currentState = State.Error;
1716 throw;
1717 }
1718 }
1719
1720 public override void WriteEndAttribute()
1721 {
1722 try
1723 {
1724 AdvanceState(Token.EndAttribute);
1725 if (_specAttr != 0)
1726 {
1727 switch (_specAttr)
1728 {
1729 case SpecialAttribute.DefaultXmlns:
1730 {
1731 string stringValue = _attrValueCache.StringValue;
1732 if (PushNamespaceExplicit(string.Empty, stringValue))
1733 {
1734 if (_rawWriter != null)
1735 {
1736 if (_rawWriter.SupportsNamespaceDeclarationInChunks)
1737 {
1738 _rawWriter.WriteStartNamespaceDeclaration(string.Empty);
1739 _attrValueCache.Replay(_rawWriter);
1740 _rawWriter.WriteEndNamespaceDeclaration();
1741 }
1742 else
1743 {
1744 _rawWriter.WriteNamespaceDeclaration(string.Empty, stringValue);
1745 }
1746 }
1747 else
1748 {
1749 _writer.WriteStartAttribute(string.Empty, "xmlns", "http://www.w3.org/2000/xmlns/");
1750 _attrValueCache.Replay(_writer);
1751 _writer.WriteEndAttribute();
1752 }
1753 }
1754 _curDeclPrefix = null;
1755 break;
1756 }
1757 case SpecialAttribute.PrefixedXmlns:
1758 {
1759 string stringValue = _attrValueCache.StringValue;
1760 if (stringValue.Length == 0)
1761 {
1762 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Xml_PrefixForEmptyNs);
1763 }
1764 if (stringValue == "http://www.w3.org/2000/xmlns/" || (stringValue == "http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace" && _curDeclPrefix != "xml"))
1765 {
1766 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Xml_CanNotBindToReservedNamespace);
1767 }
1768 if (PushNamespaceExplicit(_curDeclPrefix, stringValue))
1769 {
1770 if (_rawWriter != null)
1771 {
1772 if (_rawWriter.SupportsNamespaceDeclarationInChunks)
1773 {
1774 _rawWriter.WriteStartNamespaceDeclaration(_curDeclPrefix);
1775 _attrValueCache.Replay(_rawWriter);
1776 _rawWriter.WriteEndNamespaceDeclaration();
1777 }
1778 else
1779 {
1780 _rawWriter.WriteNamespaceDeclaration(_curDeclPrefix, stringValue);
1781 }
1782 }
1783 else
1784 {
1785 _writer.WriteStartAttribute("xmlns", _curDeclPrefix, "http://www.w3.org/2000/xmlns/");
1786 _attrValueCache.Replay(_writer);
1787 _writer.WriteEndAttribute();
1788 }
1789 }
1790 _curDeclPrefix = null;
1791 break;
1792 }
1793 case SpecialAttribute.XmlSpace:
1794 {
1795 _attrValueCache.Trim();
1796 string stringValue = _attrValueCache.StringValue;
1797 if (stringValue == "default")
1798 {
1799 _elemScopeStack[_elemTop].xmlSpace = XmlSpace.Default;
1800 }
1801 else
1802 {
1803 if (!(stringValue == "preserve"))
1804 {
1805 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Format(System.SR.Xml_InvalidXmlSpace, stringValue));
1806 }
1807 _elemScopeStack[_elemTop].xmlSpace = XmlSpace.Preserve;
1808 }
1809 _writer.WriteStartAttribute("xml", "space", "http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace");
1810 _attrValueCache.Replay(_writer);
1811 _writer.WriteEndAttribute();
1812 break;
1813 }
1814 case SpecialAttribute.XmlLang:
1815 {

2550 private void PushNamespaceImplicit(string prefix, string ns)
2551 {

2553 NamespaceKind kind;
2554 if (num != -1)
2555 {

2557 {

2559 {

2561 {
2562 prefix,
2563 _nsStack[num].namespaceUri,
2564 ns
2565 });

2568 }
2569 if (_nsStack[num].kind == NamespaceKind.Special)
2570 {
2571 if (!(prefix == "xml"))
2572 {
2573 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Xml_XmlnsPrefix);

2576 {
2577 throw new ArgumentException(System.SR.Xml_XmlPrefix);

2753 private void AdvanceState(Token token)
2754 {
2755 if (_currentState >= State.Closed)
2756 {
2757 if (_currentState == State.Closed || _currentState == State.Error)
2758 {
2759 throw new InvalidOperationException(System.SR.Xml_ClosedOrError);
2760 }
2761 throw new InvalidOperationException(System.SR.Format(System.SR.Xml_WrongToken, tokenName[(int)token], GetStateName(_currentState)));
2762 }
2763 State state;
2764 while (true)
2765 {
2766 state = _stateTable[(int)(((int)token << 4) + _currentState)];
2767 switch (state)
2768 {
2769 case State.Error:
2770 ThrowInvalidStateTransition(token, _currentState);
2771 break;
2772 case State.StartContent:
2773 StartElementContent();
2774 state = State.Content;
2775 break;
2776 case State.StartContentEle:
2777 StartElementContent();
2778 state = State.Element;
2779 break;
2780 case State.StartContentB64:
2781 StartElementContent();
2782 state = State.B64Content;
2783 break;

4246 private Task AdvanceStateAsync(Token token)
4247 {
4248 if (_currentState >= State.Closed)
4249 {
4250 if (_currentState == State.Closed || _currentState == State.Error)
4251 {
4252 throw new InvalidOperationException(System.SR.Xml_ClosedOrError);
4253 }
4254 throw new InvalidOperationException(System.SR.Format(System.SR.Xml_WrongToken, tokenName[(int)token], GetStateName(_currentState)));
4255 }
4256 State state;
4257 while (true)
4258 {
4259 state = _stateTable[(int)(((int)token << 4) + _currentState)];
4260 switch (state)
4261 {
4262 case State.Error:
4263 ThrowInvalidStateTransition(token, _currentState);
4264 break;
4265 case State.StartContent:
4266 return AdvanceStateAsync_ReturnWhenFinish(StartElementContentAsync(), State.Content);
4267 case State.StartContentEle:
4268 return AdvanceStateAsync_ReturnWhenFinish(StartElementContentAsync(), State.Element);
4269 case State.StartContentB64:
4270 return AdvanceStateAsync_ReturnWhenFinish(StartElementContentAsync(), State.B64Content);
4271 case State.StartDoc:
4272 return AdvanceStateAsync_ReturnWhenFinish(WriteStartDocumentAsync(), State.Document);
4273 case State.StartDocEle:
4274 return AdvanceStateAsync_ReturnWhenFinish(WriteStartDocumentAsync(), State.Element);
4275 case State.EndAttrSEle:
4276 {
4277 Task task = SequenceRun(WriteEndAttributeAsync(), (XmlWellFormedWriter thisRef) => thisRef.StartElementContentAsync(), this);
4278 return AdvanceStateAsync_ReturnWhenFinish(task, State.Element);
4279 }
4280 case State.EndAttrEEle:
4281 {
4282 Task task = SequenceRun(WriteEndAttributeAsync(), (XmlWellFormedWriter thisRef) => thisRef.StartElementContentAsync(), this);
4283 return AdvanceStateAsync_ReturnWhenFinish(task, State.Content);
4284 }
4285 case State.EndAttrSCont:
4286 {
4287 Task task = SequenceRun(WriteEndAttributeAsync(), (XmlWellFormedWriter thisRef) => thisRef.StartElementContentAsync(), this);
4288 return AdvanceStateAsync_ReturnWhenFinish(task, State.Content);
4289 }
4290 case State.EndAttrSAttr:
4291 return AdvanceStateAsync_ReturnWhenFinish(WriteEndAttributeAsync(), State.Attribute);
4292 case State.PostB64Cont:
4293 if (_rawWriter != null)
4294 {
4295 return AdvanceStateAsync_ContinueWhenFinish(_rawWriter.WriteEndBase64Async(), State.Content, token);
4296 }
4297 _currentState = State.Content;
4298 continue;
4299 case State.PostB64Attr:
4300 if (_rawWriter != null)
4301 {
4302 return AdvanceStateAsync_ContinueWhenFinish(_rawWriter.WriteEndBase64Async(), State.Attribute, token);
4303 }
4304 _currentState = State.Attribute;
4305 continue;
4306 case State.PostB64RootAttr:
4307 if (_rawWriter != null)
4308 {
4309 return AdvanceStateAsync_ContinueWhenFinish(_rawWriter.WriteEndBase64Async(), State.RootLevelAttr, token);
4310 }
4311 _currentState = State.RootLevelAttr;
4312 continue;
4313 case State.StartFragEle:
4314 StartFragment();
4315 state = State.Element;
4316 break;
4317 case State.StartFragCont:
4318 StartFragment();
4319 state = State.Content;
4320 break;
4321 case State.StartFragB64:
4322 StartFragment();
4323 state = State.B64Content;
4324 break;
4325 case State.StartRootLevelAttr:
4326 return AdvanceStateAsync_ReturnWhenFinish(WriteEndAttributeAsync(), State.RootLevelAttr);
4327 }
4328 break;
4329 }
4330 _currentState = state;
4331 return Task.CompletedTask;
4332 }

4363 protected override async ValueTask DisposeAsyncCore()
4364 {
4365 if (_currentState == State.Closed)
4366 {
4367 return;
4368 }
4369 try
4370 {
4371 if (_writeEndDocumentOnClose)
4372 {
4373 while (_currentState != State.Error && _elemTop > 0)
4374 {
4375 await WriteEndElementAsync().ConfigureAwait(continueOnCapturedContext: false);
4376 }
4377 }
4378 else if (_currentState != State.Error && _elemTop > 0)
4379 {
4380 try
4381 {
4382 await AdvanceStateAsync(Token.EndElement).ConfigureAwait(continueOnCapturedContext: false);
4383 }
4384 catch
4385 {
4386 _currentState = State.Error;
4387 throw;
4388 }
4389 }
4390 if (InBase64 && _rawWriter != null)

4392 await _rawWriter.WriteEndBase64Async().ConfigureAwait(continueOnCapturedContext: false);
4393 }
4394 await _writer.FlushAsync().ConfigureAwait(continueOnCapturedContext: false);
4395 }
4396 finally
4397 {
4398 try
4399 {
